description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from J-POP, ANIME, VTuber!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Pray *locked
・Memeshikute / Golden Bomber
・Zenryoku Batankyu / AOP
・RDY / RYO, POCYOMUKIN, Heartbeat & GP
・Again And Again / GAKI RANGER feat. UMEDA CYPHER
・Monster / YOASOBI
・My Angle / Hanabasami Kyo
・Operation Neverland / Nekomiya Hinata
・We Are Vox Monsters / VOMS Project
・Second Sight Stella / Kagura Nana

■Navigator
・Nekomiya Hinata *with voice
・Kagura Nana *with voice

■Avatar
・Hinata(2D)
・Nana(2D)
・Hinata(VirtuaREAL)
・Nana(VirtuaREAL)
・Kyo(VirtuaREAL)
・Pikamee(VirtuaREAL)
・Tomoshika(VirtuaREAL)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Hit Song + VTuber Pack 3
